              },
              "Text": {
                "type": "cexolocstring",
                "value": {
                  "0": "You have agreed to help out the Miller of Bree with his lost son and shipment of Ale.The miller said that his son and the shipment was destined for Tharbad along the South Greenway Road."
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "__struct_id": 1,
              "End": {
                "type": "word",
                "value": 0
              },
              "ID": {
                "type": "dword",
                "value": 2
              },
              "Text": {
                "type": "cexolocstring",
                "value": {
                  "0": "Having taken care of the grim business of delivering the bad news to the Miller. His grieve will hold with him till the next harvest. But perphaps he can find solace in his wife and the Ale he makes."
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
