                "value": 1
              },
              "Text": {
                "type": "cexolocstring",
                "value": {
                  "0": "Elrond has bade me do two tasks.1. To Break the siege of the Urukai into the Trollshallls and bring back the Helm of Azog the Warlord.2. Venture into Moria and find some sign of Balin's Expidition."
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "__struct_id": 1,
              "End": {
                "type": "word",
                "value": 0
              },
              "ID": {
                "type": "dword",
                "value": 2
              },
              "Text": {
                "type": "cexolocstring",
                "value": {
                  "0": "My missions to Elrond have been completed, I now have a new place to call home."
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
