                "value": 0
              },
              "ID": {
                "type": "dword",
                "value": 1
              },
              "Text": {
                "type": "cexolocstring",
                "value": {
                  "0": "I am to help the Temple Illuvatar feed the hungry citizens of Tharbad. I am to purchase venison from the local general store.And proceed to the bridge of Tharbad.There the hungry refugees await.Imust feed 20 of them to recieve compensation."
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "__struct_id": 1,
              "End": {
                "type": "word",
                "value": 0
              },
              "ID": {
                "type": "dword",
                "value": 2
              },
              "Text": {
                "type": "cexolocstring",
                "value": {
                  "0": "The downtroden refugees will not loose sleep over muscle spasms brought on by hunger.Their children will not wither and die.You have given selflessly for a noble cause and overcome another side affect of the war against Sauron."
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
