              "Text": {
                "type": "cexolocstring",
                "value": {
                  "0": "An old woman in Bree told me to seek out the Ruins of Annuminas which lay North along the Greenway Pass. Once an ancient realm of the Dunandain, I might be able to seek adventuring uncovering it's mysteries."
                }
              }
            }
