      {
        "__struct_id": 8,
        "Comment": {
          "type": "cexostring",
          "value": ""
        },
        "EntryList": {
          "type": "list",
          "value": [
            {
              "__struct_id": 0,
              "End": {
                "type": "word",
                "value": 1
              },
              "ID": {
                "type": "dword",
                "value": 1
              },
              "Text": {
                "type": "cexolocstring",
                "value": {
                  "0": "===  Server Rules ===\nThese rules must be sctrictly and specifically followed, there is no loop hole to trick the rules. Please abide to the rules as much as you can.\n\n1) Never use Cheats or do Cheats of any kind, that INCLUDES item duplicating of any kind and even the lesser kind of cheating. DMs and Mods will be keeping an eye on the Server. We Know them all. If you know any, don't Abuse them. .2da editing is not allowed, YOU WILL BE COUGHT.Report them and you'll be rewarded accordingly.\n\n2) No swearing on shout, incase you dont know what it means, swearing is cursing, bad words, insults, anything stupid. Use shout frequently and for GOOD purposes.\n\n3) If you loose items, please talk to a DM about it. Remember you won't always get the items you lost back. So unless your reason is REASONABLE then you will be helped. No not complaining!\n\n4) And when in a Guild PLEASE YOU MUST FOLLOW SERVER RULES 1- 10 + Guild RULES!!!! Braking this rule will cause you to loose your Membership in a Guild. Same applies to Leaders\n\n5)  Although Role Playing is not required, people that Role Play to any extent are often the most likely to be chosen Ranked in the Hall of Legends, rewards will come in handy.\n\n6) PVP - REMEMBER when you just killed some creature who dropped something you all want, never ninja loot it...remember to ROLL FOR IT, whoever rolls the highest gets it. Its only fair. Thats why I made that Roll script in the emote wand. NINJA LOOTING IS PATETHIC, do not do it. You may not ninja loot your own party or Guild members. Pick Pocketing IS NOT ALLOWED IN THE ARENA AT ANY TIME. Ransoming someones items is not required, but encouraged. Ransoming is Role Playing, and Role Playing gets you Ranks and reward. Monk Speed Thieves are not welcome here, but are allowed. You will simply be disputed and disliked, eventually someone will get you banned.Pick Pocketing, Disarming, and Ninja Looting are all allowed. But as I said, you will simply be disputed and disliked, eventually someone will get you banned.\n\n7) Leading NPCs to other areas by running from them or Domination are not acceptable actions here. Please do not do this, Running for your life is one this leading a NPC to other areas is another. If a creature chases you to another area, please report it to a DM immediatly.\n\n8) If you are in a Guild you MUST answer a shout for aid by an NPC of your faction. \n\n9) Do not disrespect DMs or other Players, the DM is always right.\n\n10)  Following the rules at the best of your abilities will get you rewarded.\n\n"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
